Interesting documentation:

A)
Query builder:
The following URL consist in a weather query with:
*Location: Los Angeles, CA
*Date: 01.03.2022, 01.04.2022 (today:23.03.2022)
*Unit: metrics
*Include: historical observations (obs), forecast as history (histfcst), forecast (fcst), statistical forecast (stats), current conditions (current)

URL:
https://weather.visualcrossing.com/VisualCrossingWebServices/rest/services/timeline/Los%20Angeles?unitGroup=metric&key=Z3Z4Q9PHE3MSXWKUPQNQ8434D&include=obs%2Cfcst%2Cstats%2Chours%2Ccurrent%2Chistfcst
